actions.description: Search the web for relevant content.
actions.name: braveSearch

properties.description: The users search query term. Query can not be empty. Maximum of 400 characters and 50 words in the query.
properties.label: Search Query
properties.name: q

properties.description: The number of search results returned in response. The maximum is 20. The actual number delivered may be less than requested. Combine this parameter with offset to paginate search results.
properties.label: Count
properties.name: count

properties.description: The zero based offset that indicates number of search result pages (count) to skip before returning the result. The actual number delivered may be less than requested.
properties.label: Offset
properties.name: offset

properties.description: The level of safe search filtering applied to the query.
properties.label: Safe Search
properties.name: safesearch

properties.description: Filters search results by when they were discovered.
properties.label: Freshness
properties.name: freshness

properties.description: A comma delimited string of result types to include in the search response.
properties.label: Result Filter
properties.name: result_filter

properties.description: This parameter enables summary key generation in web search results.
properties.label: Summary
properties.name: summary

properties.description: Whether to apply search operators
properties.label: Operators
properties.name: operators

properties.description: The 2 character country code where the search results come from.
properties.label: Country
properties.name: country

properties.description: The 2 or more character language code for which the search results are provided.
properties.label: Search Language
properties.name: search_lang
